he downloaded digital files. just unzip the file, and you’ll be ready to start using your purchase!<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"collapsible_tab_VRFaEK":{"type":"collapsible_tab","disabled":true,"settings":{"open_first_collapsible_row":false,"heading":"How to install theme to shopify","icon":"question_mark","content":"<p><strong>How to install theme to shopify<\/strong><\/p><p>When you’re purchase any theme from roarecipe.com<\/p><ul><li>All of your purchases download <strong>links can be found in email<\/strong> you receive immediately after you make payment. You can also find this page link in order confirmation email you receive after purchasing. You can download products clicking “Download Now.<\/li><\/ul><p><\/p><ul><li>After clicking “Download Now\" button you will download a zip file which includes all the files along with theme zip file. <strong>Check Your Downloads Folder<\/strong>: Once the download is complete, go to the designated folder on your computer where the files were saved (usually the \"Downloads\" folder). You can now access and use the downloaded digital files.<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>You need to <strong>UNZIP <\/strong>that file in order to see all included files. After unzipping, you will see a folder with all the files along with theme.zip file, which can be upload to shopify. <\/li><\/ul><p><\/p><p><\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["testimonial_images_dwVMnc","2fead2d5-7a3f-49d9-bacf-1d813be9861e","title_JizAxD","8f8d8903-27e7-4cac-99c4-ec1b60b7f309","price","description_7rxnqF","variant_picker","7105577f-93d1-4b1b-9580-5c13e73776c2","quantity_selector","text_benefits_b4rAYW","text_iG36Fm","6be49df1-2de0-49c6-9f17-baef396c43c2","buy_buttons","payment_twiXY7","promo_slide_8CpDYK","ad4a2bc2-8dd2-4105-9923-5bd7d66f77f3","eb02bfdc-836f-40fa-bc36-a93ccbb6f998","d3e392fa-572e-4895-a7d3-dd12277627ff","collapsible_tab_ykbaxM","collapsible_tab_fBD87j","collapsible_tab_VRFaEK"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"enable_sticky_info":false,"show_feature_media":f